OL,3,CMother whose sons were killed by their
OL,4,Cfather says law change will save lives
OL,6,FWarning: Some people may find the
OL,7,Fdetails in this story distressing.
OL,9,FThe mother of two children killed by
OL,10,Ftheir father says a change to the law
OL,11,F"will save generations of children's
OL,12,Flives".
OL,14,FClaire Throssell's children, Jack, 12,
OL,15,Fand Paul, nine, were killed in a house
OL,16,Ffire started by their father in
OL,17,FOctober 2014, after he was granted
OL,18,Faccess to the boys.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/14
