OL,4,Cfather says law change will save lives
OL,6,FChildren exposed to family court
OL,7,Fproceedings will be protected from
OL,8,Fdomestic abuse and harm, according to
OL,9,Fnew plans announced by the government.
OL,11,FThe move will repeal the presumption
OL,12,Fof parental involvement from the
OL,13,FChildren Act 1998, which prioritises
OL,14,Fparental contact with children.
OL,16,FAssuming it is always in the best
OL,17,Finterest of the child to be involved
OL,18,Fwith both parents "can perpetuate
OL,19,Fabuse", according to new evidence
OL,20,Fpublished by the government.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/14
