OL,4,Cfather says law change will save lives
OL,6,FIf parents are thought to be a threat
OL,7,Fto their child's safety, involvement
OL,8,Fin their lives can be restricted, for
OL,9,Fexample, through courts ordering
OL,10,Fsupervised contact, involvement
OL,11,Flimited to written communication or by
OL,12,Fordering that there should be no
OL,13,Finvolvement at all.
OL,15,FJack and Paul were spending five hours
OL,16,Fof unsupervised contact with their
OL,17,Ffather, Darren Sykes, as ordered by
OL,18,Fthe court, when they were killed.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/14
