OL,6,F"I got a knock on the door by a police
OL,7,Fofficer, and as a mum, you just know,
OL,8,Fbecause I knew every time they were
OL,9,Fgoing into danger. And I said to the
OL,10,Fpolice officer straight away, 'What
OL,11,Fhas he done?' And he said there'd been
OL,12,Fan incident at the house, a fire.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/14
