OL,4,Cfather says law change will save lives
OL,6,F"But let's be clear, he'd set 14
OL,7,Fseparate fires with five canisters of
OL,8,Fpetrol, used my belongings, and set
OL,9,Ffires in the whole house. He'd
OL,10,Fbarricaded the doors and he'd put a
OL,11,Fmattress up between the living room
OL,12,Fand the kitchen. So he'd planned it
OL,13,Fdown to the last inch, to the last
OL,14,Fdegree. He was absolutely determined
OL,15,Fthat neither Jack nor Paul would come
OL,16,Fout of that house.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/14
