OL,4,Cfather says law change will save lives
OL,6,F"I have to live with the fact that he
OL,7,Fonly killed them to punish me. They
OL,8,Fonly died because of me. But equally,
OL,9,Fthey were under the protection of a
OL,10,Ffamily court, Cafcass (Children and
OL,11,FFamily Court Advisory and Support
OL,12,FService) and social services, and we
OL,13,Fwere just invisible."
OL,15,FThe government said the change to the
OL,16,Flaw follows "tireless campaigning" by
OL,17,FClaire Throssell.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/14
