OL,6,F"This doesn't feel like a victory
OL,7,Fbecause obviously the boys are not
OL,8,Fhere, and 67 children have lost their
OL,9,Flives before we got to this day. But
OL,10,Fit does feel like a day where there is
OL,11,Freal change," she said.
OL,13,F"No parents should have to hold their
OL,14,Fchildren as they die, from the abuse
OL,15,Fof a perpetrator, as I did a decade
OL,16,Fago."
