OL,6,FThe inquest into the boys' deaths
OL,7,Fheard they had been lured to Sykes's
OL,8,Fhome with a new model train set,
OL,9,Fbefore he set fire to the building,
OL,10,Falso killing himself.
OL,12,FHe had been granted access to his
OL,13,Fchildren for five hours a week,
OL,14,Fdespite Ms Throssell's evidence that
OL,15,Fhe had previously threatened to kill
OL,16,Fthem and himself.
