OL,4,Cfather says law change will save lives
OL,6,F"Decision makers need to recognise
OL,7,Fthat abuse is a pattern of behaviours,
OL,8,Fand that the potential for escalation
OL,9,Fand risk of harm is there even after
OL,10,Fthe parents' relationship has ended."
OL,12,FDeputy Prime Minister David Lammy said
OL,13,Fthe reform comes as part of the Labour
OL,14,Fgovernment's broader Plan For Change.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/14
